<p style="text-align: right;"><strong>?ואיך הולך לך בינתיים</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: right;">!ממש כיף</p>
<p style="text-align: right;">
<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"> </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/barak03-II.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-762 aligncenter" title="barak03-II" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/06/barak03-II.jpg" alt="" width="241" height="188" /></a></p>
